### 🧾 Get all users (requires valid token)
GET http://localhost:5282/api/users
Authorization: Bearer your-valid-token

###

### 🔍 Get user by ID
GET http://localhost:5282/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer your-valid-token

###

### 🔍 Get user with non-existent ID (to trigger 404 or exception)
GET http://localhost:5282/api/users/999
Authorization: Bearer your-valid-token

###

### ➕ Create user
POST http://localhost:5282/api/users
Authorization: Bearer your-valid-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Emmanuel Delgado",
  "email": "emmanuel@techhive.com",
  "department": "Engineering"
}

###

### ❌ Create user with invalid body (to trigger validation error)
POST http://localhost:5282/api/users
Authorization: Bearer your-valid-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "",
  "email": "",
  "department": ""
}

###

### ✏️ Update existing user
PUT http://localhost:5282/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer your-valid-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Emmanuel D.",
  "email": "emmanuel.d@techhive.com",
  "department": "Product"
}

###

### 🗑️ Delete user
DELETE http://localhost:5282/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer your-valid-token

###

### 🔐 Missing token (should return 401 Unauthorized)
GET http://localhost:5282/api/users

###

### 🔐 Invalid token
GET http://localhost:5282/api/users
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token